==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unnatural
<hw>Un*nat"u*ral</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not natural;
contrary, or not conforming, to the order of nature; being without
natural traits; <as>as, <ex>unnatural</ex> crimes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- See <er>Factitious</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*nat"u*ral*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un*nat"u*ral*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unnaturalize</ent>⟦br⟧
